cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Symbol

类 FuncSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Symbol.Symbol
      • cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Symbol.FuncSymbol

  • public class FuncSymbol
extends Symbol
    This derived class represents a function symbol Note that if the function has no return value, the returnType will be set as null.

      • FuncSymbol

        public FuncSymbol(Name _funcName,
                  Type _returnType,
                  java.util.List<Name> FPN,
                  java.util.List<Type> FPT)
        Creation function of funcSymbol. Define the formal parameters in the current scope
        参数:
        _funcName - the function's name
        _returnType - the function's return type (null if "void")
        FPN - the function's formal parameter Name List
        FPT - the function's formal parameter Type List
